            <div class="tool-pane">
                <h2>OAuth 2.0 Configuration</h2>
                <p class="tool-pane-intro">Select the grant type and configure the parameters to generate a corresponding sequence diagram and step-by-step breakdown.</p>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="grantType">Grant Type</label>
                    <select id="grantType" class="form-select">
                        <option value="authorization_code">Authorization Code</option>
                        <option value="implicit">Implicit</option>
                        <option value="client_credentials">Client Credentials</option>
